We first demonstrate the intermediate and collaboration representations.
A part of intermediate and collaboration representations are shown in Table¬†2.
These results indicate that the intermediate and collaboration representations do not directly approximate the features of the raw data.
Focusing on the range of values in each column, we see that the intermediate representation varies widely from institution to institution, while the collaboration representation is generally consistent.
It is not possible to recover the raw data only from the intermediate and collaboration representations.
